{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_4fc0a7448e8444b1b8cb75bd","type":"tool_result","content":"1\tWhat is it?\n2\t===========\n3\t\n4\tLFS is an online shop based on Python, Django and jQuery.\n5\t\n6\tInformation\n7\t===========\n8\t\n9\tFor more information please visit:\n10\t\n11\t* http://www.getlfs.com\n12\t\n13\tDocumentation\n14\t=============\n15\t\n16\tFor the latest documentation please visit:\n17\t\n18\t* http://docs.getlfs.com\n19\t\n20\tDemo shop\n21\t=========\n22\t\n23\tA demo shop can be tried here:\n24\t\n25\t* http://demo.getlfs.com\n26\t\n27\tDevelopment\n28\t===========\n29\t\n30\tFor development environment please visit:\n31\t\n32\t* https://github.com/diefenbach/lfs-buildout-development\n33\t\n34\tChanges\n35\t=======\n36\t\n37\t0.11.0 (2017-03-09)\n38\t-------------------\n39\t* Adds Django 1.10 support\n40\t* Excludes variants from sitemap\n41\t* Add appending slash to all urls\n42\t* Use F() expressions to update stock amount (#203)\n43\t* Use F() expression to increase use_amount for vouchers (#202)\n44\t* Removes django-pagination (use Django's default one instead)\n45\t* remove STATIC_URL (user static_url tag instead)\n46\t* fix saving properties and variant prices [pigletto]\n47\t\n48\t0.10.2 (2015-04-25)\n49\t-------------------\n50\t* Updates lfs-paypal to 1.3\n51\t* Fixes all tests\n52\t\n53\t0.10.1 (2015-04-23)\n54\t-------------------\n55\t* Fixes MANIFEST.in\n56\t* Fixes adding and display of reviews when L10N is turned on\n57\t\n58\t0.10.0 (2015-04-22)\n59\t-------------------\n60\t* Adds Django 1.8 support\n61\t* Moves static files to lfs.manage\n62\t* Moves manage templates to lfs.manage\n63\t\n64\tHISTORY\n65\t=======\n66\t\n67\tFor the complete history please look into HISTORY.txt\n68\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f40d81cd-a8e1-4d99-9824-3e751d9ffb35","uuid":"23b15cb4-656f-45d7-9271-081fbc73dd7f","timestamp":"2026-04-08T21:52:11.702Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspace/README.rst","content":"What is it?\n===========\n\nLFS is an online shop based on Python, Django and jQuery.\n\nInformation\n===========\n\nFor more information please visit:\n\n* http://www.getlfs.com\n\nDocumentation\n=============\n\nFor the latest documentation please visit:\n\n* http://docs.getlfs.com\n\nDemo shop\n=========\n\nA demo shop can be tried here:\n\n* http://demo.getlfs.com\n\nDevelopment\n===========\n\nFor development environment please visit:\n\n* https://github.com/diefenbach/lfs-buildout-development\n\nChanges\n=======\n\n0.11.0 (2017-03-09)\n-------------------\n* Adds Django 1.10 support\n* Excludes variants from sitemap\n* Add appending slash to all urls\n* Use F() expressions to update stock amount (#203)\n* Use F() expression to increase use_amount for vouchers (#202)\n* Removes django-pagination (use Django's default one instead)\n* remove STATIC_URL (user static_url tag instead)\n* fix saving properties and variant prices [pigletto]\n\n0.10.2 (2015-04-25)\n-------------------\n* Updates lfs-paypal to 1.3\n* Fixes all tests\n\n0.10.1 (2015-04-23)\n-------------------\n* Fixes MANIFEST.in\n* Fixes adding and display of reviews when L10N is turned on\n\n0.10.0 (2015-04-22)\n-------------------\n* Adds Django 1.8 support\n* Moves static files to lfs.manage\n* Moves manage templates to lfs.manage\n\nHISTORY\n=======\n\nFor the complete history please look into HISTORY.txt\n","numLines":68,"startLine":1,"totalLines":68}}}
